{"name": "fild-api-hub", "metadata": {"name": "fild-api-hub", "version": "0.0.5", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/elenakulgavaya/fild-api-hub", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["deepdiff", "fild", "requests", "pyyaml", "waiting"], "summary": "Library to operate api with help of fild contracts", "upload_time": 1733736075}, "documentation": ["# fild-api-hub\n\nThe FILD Api Hub is a set of tools enabling using FILD described contracts\nin tests. \n\nConfigure your project with yaml files in `etc/config.yaml` containing\n```yaml\nApp:\n  url: http://localhost:8000\nMockServer:\n  host: localhost\n  port: 8088\n```\n\nOverride any local configuration variables by adding `etc/local.yaml`\n```yaml\nMockServer:\n  port: 8080\n```\n\nUse `ApiMethod` to describe the API \n```python\nfrom fild.sdk import Dictionary, Int, String, Uuid\nfrom fildapi import ApiMethod, HttpMethod\n\n\nSERVICE = 'customer_api'\nBASE_URL = 'http://mydomain.customerapi'\n\n\nclass CreateUserRequest(Dictionary):\n    Name = String(name='name')\n    Email = String(name='email')\n    Age = Int(name='age', min_val=18, max_val=120)\n\n    \nclass CreateUserResponse(Dictionary):\n    Id = Uuid(name='id')\n\n    \nclass CreateUser(ApiMethod):\n    method = HttpMethod.POST\n    url = 'api/users'\n    req_body = CreateUserRequest\n    resp_body = CreateUserResponse\n```\n\nUse `ApiMethod` for mocking and verifying integrations\n```python\nfrom customer_api import CreateUser\n\n\ndef test_failed_to_create_user():\n    CreateUser.reply(status=400)\n    # Test action to check error\n\n\ndef test_verify_call_to_customer_api():\n    CreateUser.reply()\n    # Some test action\n    CreateUser.verify_called()\n```\n\nUse `ApiCaller` to test the api:\n```python\nfrom fildapi import ApiCaller\nfrom customer_api import CreateUser\n\n\nclass CreateUserCall(ApiCaller):\n    method = CreateUser\n\n\ndef test_create_user():\n    CreateUserCall().request().verify_response()\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "fildapi", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "fildapi.ApiCaller", "xref": {"fqname": "fildapi.caller.ApiCaller", "project": null}}, {"name": "fildapi.ApiMethod", "xref": {"fqname": "fildapi.method.ApiMethod", "project": null}}, {"name": "fildapi.HttpMethod", "xref": {"fqname": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod", "project": null}}, {"name": "fildapi.MockServer", "xref": {"fqname": "fildapi.mock.service.MockServer", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "fildapi.schema", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "fildapi.schema.get_default_app_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod", "bases": ["Enum"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.POST", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.GET", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.HEAD", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.PATCH", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.DELETE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.PUT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.TRACE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.HttpMethod.OPTIONS", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.Schema", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "fildapi.schema.Schema.get_relative_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "path_params", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "fildapi.schema.Schema.get_service_name", "asynchronou